title: Brand New 2 BEDROOM TH in Highland Park * Recessed Lights * Must See
posting_body: ['Unit Availability: September 5, 2022', 'Welcome to Fig & York where design-centric living is the focus.', 'Enjoy live/work loft-style units with high ceilings throughout.', 'Fig & York offers features such as covered gated parking, fully equipped gym, secure package locker room, central heat and air, in-unit washer and dryer, EV charging stations, outdoor courtyard, and much more!', 'While living at Fig & York, you will never go hungry.', 'We are blocks away from Amara Kitchen, Go Get Em Tiger, Triple Beam Pizza, Kitchen Mouse, and several more eateries that will keep your taste buds satisfied!', 'Located between Pasadena and Downtown LA, Highland Park is a short 15-minute drive in either direction.', 'Alternatively, the Metro stop is located a short walk away, making it convenient to be able to live car-free.', 'It would be our pleasure to show you our latest project.', 'Schedule your tour today.', 'Features Include:', '- Central Heat and Air', '- Large Built-in Closets', '- EV Charging Stations', '- Outdoor Courtyard', '- Recessed Lights', '- Stainless Steel Appliances', '- Fully Equipped Gym - Surveillance Camera Throughout', '- Generous Ceiling Heights Throughout', '- Washer/Dryer in unit', '- Stained and Polished Concrete Floors', '- High Walkscore', '- Gated Package Locker Room', '- Balcony', '- Covered Gated Parking', 'Pet-Friendly:', 'Pets Welcome.', 'Additional Fees and Deposit May Apply.', 'Call for Details and Restrictions.', 'Call:', 'show contact info', '6417-6422 North Figueroa Street Los Angeles, CA 90042', 'Square Feet may not be exact.', 'Price & availability are conditional.']
